{"tid":813546,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍男子車內燒炭 留遺書疑財務困擾","createTime":"2018-09-10T13:48:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T13:48:02.000Z","uid":29627,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bf2ea8f78704a13dafb9cd6fc3f978d7009f97d8","tid":813546,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T13:48:02.000Z","msg":"天水圍男子車內燒炭 留遺書疑財務困擾 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180910/large/1536548555_d5aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180910%2Flarge%2F1536548555_d5aa.jpg&h=d66f234e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【13:50】死者姓龐51歲<br />\n【11:30】警方失蹤人口組及死者兩男1女親友到場認屍，確認死者已報失蹤一個星期<br />\n<br />\n天水圍天慈路30號燒烤場附近路邊，早上8時50分，有途人行經發現，一名男子昏迷在七人車內，於是報警。救援人員到場，經檢驗證實男事主已告不治。警方封鎖調查，在車內發現有燒炭痕迹，同時撿獲遺書，大意透露生意周轉不靈，欠債數百萬元。<br />\n<br />\n現場所見，死者蓄平頭裝，穿著裇衫、西褲和皮鞋。他坐在中間左邊乘客位，左大腿已見腐爛，車頭亦舖滿枯葉，相信死去已經一段時間。死者是本地人，警方正聯絡其家人趕到現場。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/10/Kjlmsk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2FKjlmsk.png&h=5034568b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/09/10/y0ZA16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F09%2F10%2Fy0ZA16.png&h=4aa41315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180910/large/1536545808_bb1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180910%2Flarge%2F1536545808_bb1a.jpg&h=218b0b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180910/58664051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664051&d=nxdefjDRBkq1KAagcTCPl04boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=a56c8e1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180910%2F58664051&h=377de64a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180910/58664051</a>"}]}